



<div xmlns:tei="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:teix="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples" class="poem">             
   
   <div class="title"><span class="space" style="padding-left:2.0em"> </span>poem II<div class="runover" style="left:2.0em">on scotland</div>
   <span class="lg-stanza">
      <span class="l"><span class="space" style="padding-left:0.8em"> </span><span class="doubleletter-fill">O</span> what a change from<div class="runover" style="left:2.0em">pretty <span class="placeName-PERTH">perth</span> so near</div></span><br/>
      <span class="l">to dreary heather and to<div class="g-justification" style="width:NaNem"> </div><div class="runover" style="left:2.8em">streams so clear</div></span><br/>
      <span class="l">to rocks and stones upon the<span class="del-erasure"><div class="add-below" style="left:9.2em">dreary way</div></span><div class="runover" style="left:2.8em">dreary way</div></span><br/>
      <span class="l">no sun is shining as on <span class="del-erasure">sprig</span><div class="runover" style="left:2.4em">sprightly may</div></span><br/>
      <span class="l">again it changes to the<div class="runover" style="left:2.8em">winding <span class="geogName-EARN">ern</span><span class="glosses"><a href="../glosses/on_scotland_glosses.php#ERNGLOSS" target="_blank">1</a></span></div></span><br/>
      <span class="l">tis shallow water but it has<div class="runover" style="left:3.6em"><span class="subst-del">i</span><span class="subst-add-overwriting">n</span>o fern</div></span><br/>
      <span class="l">but it is precious for its<div class="g-justification" style="width:NaNem"> </div><div class="runover" style="left:2.8em">shining <span class="subst-del"><span class="unclear-CWB">pearls</span></span><span class="subst-add-overwriting">drops</span></div></span><br/>
      <span class="l">and <span class="subst-del"><span class="unclear-CWB">tis a river that has</span></span><span class="subst-add-overwriting">sometimes from the</span><div class="runover" style="left:2.0em"><span class="del-erasure"><span class="unclear-CWB"><span class="gap" style="padding-left:0.4em"> </span>la<span class="gap-illegible" style="padding-left: 2em"></span></span></span>
         <div id="1229145r" class="pb"></div>
         <div class="pageNum-top"><span class="space" style="padding-left:7.6em"> </span>101</div><br/>
         <span class="space" style="padding-left:1.2em"> </span><span class="geogName-EARN">river</span> a fish pops</div></span><br/>
      <span class="l"><span class="space" style="padding-left:0.8em"> </span>again it changes to a steep<div class="runover" style="left:2.0em">steep hill</div></span><br/>
      <span class="l"><span class="space" style="padding-left:0.4em"> </span>and it is cold do any thi<span class="subst-del"><span class="unclear-CWB">g</span></span><span class="subst-add-overwriting">n</span>g<div class="runover" style="left:3.2em">you will</div></span><br/>
      <span class="l">in short such changes<div class="runover" style="left:2.4em"><span class="placeName-SCOTLAND">scotland</span> does <span class="subst-del">m</span><span class="subst-add-overwriting">no</span>w take</div></span><br/>
      <span class="l">that I can&#x02BC;t tell them an<span class="subst-del"><span class="space" style="padding-left:0.4em"> </span>I</span><span class="subst-add-overwriting">d<span class="space" style="padding-left:0.4em"> </span>I</span><div class="runover">quickly end<span class="glosses"><a href="../glosses/on_scotland_glosses.php#COLLINGWOODSENDGLOSS" target="_blank">2</a></span></div></span><br/>
      </span>
   
</div>


